short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Extension to add sources to the deep

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Easily add sources to your DEEP project from the comfort of your own browser.
Using this extension you can add URLs directly to your DEEP project without having to deal with copying and pasting any URLs.

The extension will also automatically extract information for fields such as title, publisher and date (this works on most websites, however some are not entirely compatible).

Read about our privacy policy here: https://app.thedeep.io/extension-privacy-policy

Any questions? Contact admin@thedeep.io

Need help getting started with DEEP and this extension? Checkout our user guide [https://deephelp.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/categories/360000874911-DEEP-User-Guide]
